summary: Marvel Challenge → mcu characters [3/10] ♡ Natasha Romanoff  When I first joined S.H.I.E.L.D., I thought it was going straight....
caption:
Marvel Challenge → mcu characters [3/10] ♡ Natasha Romanoff

When I first joined S.H.I.E.L.D., I thought it was going straight. But I guess I just traded in the KGB for HYDRA. I thought I knew whose lies I was telling, but… I guess I can’t tell the difference anymore.
